        public String run​(List<String> tokens)
        Will take in a csv file containing stars, parse it, and store a list of Star objects.
        Specified by:
        run in interface ICallable
        Parameters:
        tokens - which should just be the name of a csv file which should contain stars
        Returns:
        String which will either contain an error message or, if successful, will indicate the number of stars loaded in.
